snippet.title: Marvel’s Spider-Man: Turf Wars – DLC 2 Teaser | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/marvels-spider-man/?emcid=or-1s-412983

Spider-Man must put an end to the turf war erupting between the Maggia crime family and gang leader Hammerhead before Marvel’s New York becomes its greatest casualty. 

Marvel's Spider-Man: Turf Wars is available for download on the PlayStation®4 system November 20, 2018. 

Marvel’s Spider-Man: The City That Never Sleeps is downloadable content for Marvel’s Spider-Man; may be sold separately. Marvel’s Spider-Man required to play associated downloadable content. Footage from Marvel’s Spider-Man: Turf Wars shown.
